    "body": "## Motivation\r\n\r\n<!-- Explain the purpose of this PR and the goals it aims to achieve. -->\r\n\r\n## Modifications\r\n\r\nIn the current implementation, `padded_scales` is initialized with shape `(B, M_padded, K_padded)`, but later reshaped to `(B, M, K)` or `(M, K)` depending on `scale_ndim`. This leads to a mismatch and potential runtime errors or incorrect memory alignment, especially during NVFP4 quantized inference using ModelOpt in SGLang.\r\n\r\n",
    "created_at": "2025-08-04T12:40:41Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-08-12T06:44:40Z",
